Searching for a movie of a specific rating, runtime, genre
If log in succesful, the user will be taken to the main page where there will be multiple filters where the user can input a specific rating, runtime or genre. The 
user can then type in the specific runtime, which if it is not in an accepted format will give them an error message. The genre and rating will be a dropdown which the 
user can click on. There will be a search button to be clicked once the user has all the specified filters they want. Once it is clicked, all the searches will show up 
and categorized. The user can then click on each one and read more about it. 
